button-radius cheatsheet:

border-radius: 50%; - Perfect circle (50% of the element's width and height).

border-radius: 5px; - Rounded corners with a fixed radius of 5 pixels.

border-radius: 50% 10px / 20px; - Elliptical shape with a horizontal radius of 50% and a vertical radius of 10 pixels, 
								  with a corner curve size of 20 pixels.

border-radius: {a_very_high_value}px; - capsule shaped.
